leve.name: Bridges of Qiqirn Country
leve.description: The engineer corps has been delayed by a sandstorm, and the supply party can no longer tarry to guard the materials delivered for repairs to the bridge near Broken Water. Yet it would be madness to leave the materials unprotected, for Qiqirn bandits call this area their own. Hold off the thieving beastmen and guard the supplies.
leve.client: The Immortal Flames 1st Corps of Engineers
